OL,2,MIntroduction to Urban Exploration
OL,4,CBash
OL,5,CSun 11:00-11:40
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GUrban Exploration or ‘Urbexing’ is
OL,9,Gexploration of manmade structures –
OL,10,Gpredominantly abandoned or derelict
OL,11,Gbuildings. This talk will introduce
OL,12,Gyou Urban Exploration, aimed at
OL,13,Gnovices who want to start or those
OL,14,Gjust curious about the practicalities
OL,15,Gof the hobby. Among other things I’ll
OL,16,Gcover how to prepare, what to bring,
OL,17,Ghow to scout and find locations and a
OL,18,Gfrank discussion of the legality and
OL,19,Gsafety (or lackthereof). The latter
OL,20,Gtwo points especially, much as I enjoy
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
